---
title: Chicken Schnitzel Plates with Dill-Garlic Smashed Potatoes and Apple Slaw
description: Comfort food at its finest! Our chicken schnitzel recipe has all the fixings you want, with herbaceous smashed potatoes, crisp and bright apple slaw and the creamy zip of Dijonnaise to bring it all together!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/schnitzels-de-poulet-203ddc6e.jpg
